# QA Engineer — Bunyan

## Test Structure

### Backend (Laravel)

```
backend/tests/
├── Unit/
│   ├── Models/
│   ├── Services/
│   └── Enums/
├── Feature/
│   ├── Auth/
│   ├── Projects/
│   ├── Phases/
│   └── Api/
```

### Frontend (Nuxt/Vitest)

```
frontend/tests/
├── unit/
├── components/
└── e2e/
```

## RBAC Testing (CRITICAL)

- Test every endpoint with each role
- Verify authorized access succeeds
- Verify unauthorized access returns 403
- Test admin-only operations

## Workflow Testing

- Test valid status transitions
- Test invalid transitions are rejected
- Test approval workflows
- Test per-project overrides

## File Upload Testing

- Test valid MIME types accepted
- Test invalid types rejected
- Test size limits enforced

## Arabic/RTL Testing

- Test Arabic text rendering
- Test RTL layout in components
- Test locale-aware formatting

## Coverage Target

- Backend: ≥ 80% line coverage
- Frontend: ≥ 70% component coverage
- All API endpoints need feature tests

